gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Hi! Sorry to keep you waiting!\p"
	.string "Welcome to WINSTON'S BURROW!\p"
	.string "My name is BIRCH.\p"
	.string "I'm here to brief every TRAINER\n"
	.string "before the first descent.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This is what we call a “POKéMON.”\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "Deep below VERDANTURF is a\n"
	.string "10-floor trainer gauntlet.\p"
	.string "Beat the trainer on each floor,\n"
	.string "then descend to the next.\p"
	.string "The burrow restores your party\n"
	.string "after floors 3, 6, and 9.\p"
	.string "On floor 10, WINSTON waits.\n"
	.string "Defeat him to clear the run.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "For this build, your trainer record\n"
	.string "is already prepared.$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "You are set as a boy for now.$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "Your name is set as MILES\n"
	.string "for now.$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "So it's {PLAYER}{KUN}.$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Ah, okay!\p"
	.string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN}, the TRAINER\n"
	.string "taking this test run.\p"
	.string "Before floor 1, choose one\n"
	.string "level 5 partner POKéMON.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "Growlithe, Electrike, and Greavard\n"
	.string "are ready at the tunnel mouth.\p"
	.string "Pick carefully, keep winning,\n"
	.string "and use each rest stop well.\p"
	.string "Now, step into the burrow.\p"
	.string "$"
